arStrings.szText: Hıh, her gün yeni ahmaklar peydahlanıyor.
Said to yourself as you busy yourself with work. Looking over your shoulder at curious visitors to your bandit town.
Bu sefer cesetlerini nehre ben atmam. (güler) Hayatta olmaz.
